## Remarks  
 您可以取得識別資訊初始化的辨識引擎使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>如<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>物件或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>如<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>物件。  
  
 中的執行個體所傳回的資訊<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>取自<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>中的設定由**語音內容**隸屬**控制台**。  
  
 您可以使用的執行個體<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>建構的特定組態<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.%23ctor%28System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo%29>建構函式。  
  
 靜態方法<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers%2A>會傳回一份所有可用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>組態為<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>執行個體。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下列範例會驗證指定<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>以及針對允許的識別項字串<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>組態，以一份<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>物件。  
  
 如果<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>和識別項字串有效，而且此範例會建立的新執行個體<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>做為引數的執行個體。  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine SelectRecognizer(CultureInfo requiredCulture, string requiredId)   
{  
  // Select based on a specific recognizer configuration  
  SpeechRecognitionEngine speechRecognitionEngine=null;  
  foreach (RecognizerInfo config in SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers())   
  {  
    if (config.Culture.Equals(requiredCulture) && config.Id== requiredId)   
    {  
      speechRecognitionEngine = new SpeechRecognitionEngine(config);  
      break;  
    }  
  }  
  return speechRecognitionEngine;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 下列範例會實作按一下按鈕以顯示中的所有資訊<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>物件存放至<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MessageBox>。  
  
 中所包含的索引鍵/值組<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>所傳回的執行個體<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo.AdditionalInfo%2A>會串連成文字表格。  
  
```csharp  
private void recognizerInfoButton_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)   
{  
  RecognizerInfo info = _recognizer.RecognizerInfo;  
  string AudioFormats = "";  
  foreach (SpeechAudioFormatInfo fmt in info.SupportedAudioFormats)   
  {  
    AudioFormats += String.Format("       {0}\n", fmt.EncodingFormat.ToString());  
  }  
  string AdditionalInfo = "";  
  foreach (string key in info.AdditionalInfo.Keys)   
  {  
    AdditionalInfo += String.Format("      {0}: {1}\n", key, info.AdditionalInfo[key]);  
  }  
  MessageBox.Show(String.Format(  
                     "Name:                 {0 } \n" +  
                     "Description:          {1} \n" +  
                     "SupportedAudioFormats:\n" +  
                     " {2} " +  
                     "Culture:              {3} \n" +  
                     "AdditionalInfo:       \n" +  
                     " {4}\n",  
                     info.Name.ToString(),  
                     info.Description.ToString(),  
                     AudioFormats,  
                     info.Culture.ToString(),  
                     AdditionalInfo));  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 A<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>物件可以包含文化特性、 相關聯的語言、 國家/地區、 使用的曆法，以及如何格式化日期和排序字串的名稱。  
  
   
  
